    FILE COMPRESSION

The original disk contains the files for Thor in a compressed format.
Specialized algorithms were chosen over the standard compression
and archiving utilities, due to the size of the DBA file (the
largest file). The resulting compression is superior to those
from the standard compression utilities tested. In addition, the
installation program which performs this decompression of files is
small (less than 15K). Compressing the DBA file using PKZIP 2.04, 
ARJ 2.30 and LHA 2.13 gave the following results (8/1993) :

   Initial Size   Spec. Alg.     PKZIP         ARJ         LHA
     1 199 484      625 349     743 928     750 879     757 488



